title: New Stars Could Emerge at 2021 U.S. Open
itunes:title: New Stars Could Emerge at 2021 U.S. Open
description:
Jon Wertheim, Executive Editor for Sports Illustrated, discusses highly ranked players opting out of the U.S. Open tennis tournament and the chances Novak Djokovic could take the calendar-year Grand Slam.

Hosts: Tim Stenovec and Katie Greifeld. Producer: Paul Brennan.
